### 🎛️ Tuning Parameters

```cpp
#define OBSTACLE_DIST    35   // Stop if object closer than 35cm
#define SIDE_CLEAR_DIST  25   // Side is "open" only if > 25cm
#define SERVO_CENTER     90   // Servo straight ahead
#define SERVO_LEFT      160   // Servo looking left
#define SERVO_RIGHT      20   // Servo looking right
#define SERVO_SETTLE    500   // Wait 500ms after servo moves
#define TURN_TIME       800   // Turn for 800ms
#define REVERSE_TIME    600   // Reverse for 600ms
#define AUTO_CLEAR_TIME 800   // Move forward 800ms to clear obstacle
```

🎚️ These are your tuning knobs. Robot stopping too early?
Increase `OBSTACLE_DIST`. Not turning enough? Increase
`TURN_TIME`. Servo overshooting? Adjust `SERVO_LEFT` and
`SERVO_RIGHT` until it points correctly.

